txt.en: 'To the north there is a large encampment known as Jâx Ugikh. This encampment is home to a variety of cultists who seem to draw their power from that place. These cultists have been attacking folks from this camp and throughout the catacombs.\n\n'Could you travel to Jâx Ugikh, explore the entrance, and drive cultists from that accursed place?'
Travel to Kên Taghlim located north of Jâx Ugikh and inform Azrât that some of the cultists have been driven off.
Talk to Azrât in Kên Taghlim
Approach the entrance to Jâx Ugikh
Travel to Jâx Ugikh, explore the grand staircase, and clear out cultists in the area.
Travel to Jâx Ugikh and explore the grand stair entrance

'The foul cultists that inhabit Jâx Ugikh present an ever-growing problem within the catacombs. These cultists have attacked supply lines, captured refugees, and continue their dark work.\n\n'Thank you for your assistance in dispatching them.'
Seek out and drive off cultists located near Jâx Ugikh.
